							We automatically group similar failures so you can stop reading the same stack trace 47 times. You're welcome.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Feature Card 4 -->
					<div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 text-left space-y-4 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all group">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-secondary/20 transition-colors">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Performance Monitoring</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
							Track latency, identify slow tool calls, and find bottlenecks. Because waiting 8 seconds for a response isn't "good enough."
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Feature Card 5 -->
					<div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 text-left space-y-4 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all group">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">OpenTelemetry Native</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
							Built on industry standards. Works with Vercel AI SDK, OpenAI Agents, and most setups. No vendor lock-in BS.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Feature Card 6 -->
					<div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 text-left space-y-4 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all group">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-accent/20 transition-colors">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z" />
							</svg>
